        <content type="html" xml:base="https://calebtrevatt.com/snippets/zola/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;context&quot;&gt;Context&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In case you weren‚Äôt aware, this whole site is built with &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.getzola.org&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Zola&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.
