&lt;p&gt;Also, shoutout to the theme creator, &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;codeberg.org&#x2F;daudix&#x2F;duckquill&quot;&gt;Daudix&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; for making this theme.
